channel.desc: Comedy 2015 A genius criminologist with OCD from Cambridge University accidentally becomes a police advisor when he's caught up in a mysterious crime on campus, however, not all his colleagues are eager for his help. Paul Piedfort, Dries Vos, Ben Miller, Barney White, Sarah Woodward, Douglas Reith, Emma Naomi, Koen De Bouw, Tanja Oostvogels, Goele Derick, Carry Goossens, Herwig Ilegems, Indra Siera.
